sentence: i need an early flight from milwaukee to denver
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', v0.departure_time, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"' FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, airport_service v3, city v4 
WHERE ((v0.departure_time BETWEEN  0 
AND  1000) AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) AND (v2.city_name = 'MILWAUKEE'))) 
AND ((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) AND (v4.city_name = 'DENVER')))));
